<S ID="289245">
It is therefore imperative that mine clearing should continue in Cambodia after the termination of UNTAC.
</S>
<S ID="289251">
463.
</S>
<S ID="289344">
A plan has been prepared for the clearance of an estimated 2 million mines in Mozambique.
